ian minority; most of its Jewish population was expelled after Israel's establishment.<annotation scu-count="0" sum-count="5" sums="14,20,29,30,44"/></line></document><document name="NYT_ENG_20050127.0071"><line>Steve Gushee writes for The Palm Beach Post.</line><line>The kidnapping of a Catholic bishop in Mosul last week is a sad reminder of the once robust but rapidly diminishing Christian community in Iraq.<annotation scu-count="1" sum-count="7" sums="0,11,21,25,30,41,51"><scu uid="5" label="the Syrian Archbishop of Mosul was kidnapped" weight="4"/></annotation></line></document></collection>